Phase115Description: I found the lockbox in the mines, thankfully still intact. I should return it to Nageed, as promised.
Callback104Header: Search for the Miner's Lockbox in Rezam's Excavation
Phase105Description: A man named Nageed asked me to retrieve a lockbox from the mines. Inside are the wages of workers like him, stolen by bandits who now plague the south. I hope there is something left to give back.
Toast: A destitute miner seeks a lost lockbox.
Name: Payment Past Due
